<h1><span id="Slav_Accepted_Alapin_Variation">Slav Accepted Alapin Variation</span></h1>
<p>The advance of the a-pawn prevents Black from controlling b5 which in turn leaves the c4 pawn available for capture.
</p>
<p><b>1.d4 d5 2.c4 c6 3.Nf3 Nf6 4.Nc3 dxc4 5. a4</b>
</p>
